A member of polycomb repressive complex 1 ( PRC1 ) , ph , contains a SAM <termsem="SO:0000417"> domain </term> at the <termsem="SO:0100015"> C-terminal </term> , and PRC1 complex is known to form <termsem="SO:0001114"> helical </term> , head-to-tail polymers through its SAM <termsem="SO:0000417"> domain </term> [ 31 ] .
