In this study , we identified a novel <termsem="SO:0000704"> gene </term> , mr-s , which encodes a SAM <termsem="SO:0000417"> domain </term> - containing protein .
The SAM <termsem="SO:0000417"> domain </term> of mr-s is most closely related to that of ph mouse <termsem="SO:0000855"> ortholog </term> , MPH1/Rae28 .
